replies.body:
{{summoner:3}}

Your 600 damage Crits are now 300 Damage crits and 150 damage autos.

You can get in and that's it. Your engage is reduced for 2.5 seconds, so by the time you've hit ulti you have to all in with no escape mechanism besides flash and you will be low HP by now being a squishy melee Carry and your only option is to flash onto enemy carry for a kill but if their support has exhaust and enemy laner has exhaust you will be exhausted on entering the fight and exhausted on flashing to the enemy ADC so will be dead or you can disengage and not play a Champion that is completely shut down by 1 summoner spell on your enemy laner.
